Functionality overview:
- sunday, do 0 level dump (date +%u)
- each day do the next level
- stamp dump with date (date +%Y%m%d)
- remove incremental dumps when they are a week old (-mtime +7)
- if there are any errors, generate output for an email

To do items
- keep one level 0 dump from each month
- allow backup up multiple volumes (right now it just does /)
- backup databases (postgres, maybe mysql)
